is absolutely amazing.

9
00:00:38,997 --> 00:00:41,417
‐ Look, we’ve been
here for two hours.

10
00:00:41,542 --> 00:00:43,212
Maybe it’s time
to call it quites

11
00:00:43,293 --> 00:00:45,303
‐ [Mint] Excuse me,
could you please open up

