(sighing)

13
00:00:46,713 --> 00:00:48,593
I know it’s after hours,
but we’re really hungry.

14
00:00:48,715 --> 00:00:50,875
‐ Now I’m starting
to get hungry,

15
00:00:51,009 --> 00:00:52,299
I should just go home.

16
00:00:52,386 --> 00:00:53,136
Huh?

17
00:00:53,220 --> 00:00:54,600
Hi‐ya‐ya‐ya!

18
00:00:54,721 --> 00:00:56,061
Argh!

19
00:00:56,181 --> 00:00:57,391
‐ Ah!

20
00:00:57,474 --> 00:00:59,144
‐ Wow, he’s cute!

21
00:00:59,226 --> 00:01:01,596
Hey, gorgeous!
‐ Huh?

22
00:01:01,728 --> 00:01:04,228
I’m sorry, I’m sorry, I’ll
get you the money soon.

