‐ Help me!

56
00:03:44,933 --> 00:03:46,643
‐ You mean those guys
are your debt collectors?

57
00:03:47,853 --> 00:03:48,693
‐ Alright!

58
00:03:49,563 --> 00:03:50,733
Yeah!

59
00:03:50,814 --> 00:03:53,524
