her a thing or two.

66
00:04:10,792 --> 00:04:11,582
Ah, uh.

67
00:04:13,503 --> 00:04:16,133
Hi‐ya‐ya‐ya‐ya‐ya‐ya‐ya‐ya!

68
00:04:16,256 --> 00:04:17,756
Hi‐ya‐ya‐ya‐ya‐ya!

69
00:04:18,967 --> 00:04:20,257
Hi‐ya!

70
00:04:20,385 --> 00:04:22,505
