‐ It’s so good,
it’ll make you cry.

82
00:04:46,453 --> 00:04:47,203
‐ Yeah?

83
00:04:47,287 --> 00:04:48,447
I guess I’ll try it too.

84
00:04:51,958 --> 00:04:52,708
Ah, ah!

85
00:04:52,793 --> 00:04:53,543
Oh, my God!

86
00:04:53,627 --> 00:04:55,497
(shouting)

87
00:04:55,629 --> 00:04:56,959
Help me!
‐ My mouth is on fire.

88
00:04:57,088 --> 00:04:58,458
‐ [Ranpha] Alright, let’s
open up, I’ll make the pizzas,

89
