‐ [Hitchhiker] Thanks a lot.

102
00:05:32,541 --> 00:05:34,711
‐ [Mint] Okay, thank you.

103
00:05:34,835 --> 00:05:35,715
Yes?

104
00:05:35,836 --> 00:05:37,416
West City, District three?

105
00:05:37,504 --> 00:05:39,264
Okay, we’ll be there shortly.

106
00:05:40,298 --> 00:05:43,798
‐ Why are there so many

107
00:05:43,885 --> 00:05:45,595
orders all of a sudden?

108
