advertising did you do?

111
00:05:53,520 --> 00:05:54,600
(laughing)

112
00:05:54,688 --> 00:05:55,398
‐ Please.

113
00:05:55,522 --> 00:05:57,522
(horns blaring)

114
00:05:57,649 --> 00:06:00,529
