could you please stop?

115
00:06:03,446 --> 00:06:04,526
‐ Hey there, babe.

116
00:06:04,656 --> 00:06:05,866
So where ya going?

117
00:06:05,949 --> 00:06:07,779
‐ Do you think it
would be possible

118
00:06:07,868 --> 00:06:09,618
