119
00:06:09,703 --> 00:06:10,833
‐ [Driver] What a nut.

120
00:06:13,874 --> 00:06:14,754
‐ What?
‐ What?

121
00:06:14,875 --> 00:06:16,045
‐ 10 minute,
‐ 10 minute,

122
00:06:16,126 --> 00:06:17,496
‐ planetary delivery?
‐ planetary delivery?

123
00:06:17,586 --> 00:06:18,746
‐ Yes.

124
00:06:18,879 --> 00:06:20,549
If we don’t deliver the
pizzas within that time,

125
00:06:20,672 --> 00:06:21,882
we take a loss.

126
00:06:21,965 --> 00:06:24,435
‐ Ah.
‐ Like the pizza’s free?

127
00:06:24,551 --> 00:06:26,051
‐ Yeah, well, that’s standard,

128
00:06:26,136 --> 00:06:28,966
but we’re actually going to
give them something extra.

129
00:06:29,055 --> 00:06:31,765
If we don’t offer our
customers something special,

130
00:06:31,892 --> 00:06:34,102
it’s next to impossible
to get orders,

131
00:06:34,227 --> 00:06:36,017
for example, if we’re
five minutes late,

132
00:06:36,104 --> 00:06:38,614
we give the customer
100 kilos of gold

133
00:06:38,732 --> 00:06:40,112
and if the pizza
is 10 minutes late,

134
00:06:40,233 --> 00:06:42,323
