resort planet.

138
00:06:47,908 --> 00:06:49,238
Unless you take some risks,

139
00:06:49,367 --> 00:06:51,197
you’re not going to
survive in this business.

140
00:06:51,286 --> 00:06:53,406
‐ You’ve gotta be kidding.
‐ You’ve gotta be kidding.

141
00:06:53,496 --> 00:06:54,996
‐ Let’s do it! (laughing)

142
00:06:55,081 --> 00:06:56,501
‐ Do it, are you kidding?

143
00:06:56,583 --> 00:06:59,673
Even if Vanilla manages to
find a delivery vehicle,

144
00:06:59,753 --> 00:07:02,763
