anything from you?

217
00:10:02,435 --> 00:10:04,845
‐ So what are you planning
to do with us then?

218
00:10:05,897 --> 00:10:08,977
‐ Well, if you’ve got no money,

219
00:10:09,109 --> 00:10:12,359
