00:10:12,445 --> 00:10:13,235
‐ [Trucker] Stop right there!

221
00:10:13,321 --> 00:10:14,451
‐ Huh?
‐ Huh?

222
00:10:14,572 --> 00:10:17,332
‐ [Repo Man] Who
the hell are you?

223
00:10:17,450 --> 00:10:20,490
