with your work, pronto!

227
00:10:27,293 --> 00:10:28,883
‐ Right!
‐ Right!

228
00:10:28,962 --> 00:10:30,252
‐ Oh, he’s so cool.

229
00:10:30,338 --> 00:10:31,548
‐ [Trucker] Ah‐huh.

230
00:10:32,757 --> 00:10:34,467
Alright, I’ll take District A.

231
00:10:34,551 --> 00:10:35,721
‐ [Trucker] I’m
off to District D.

232
00:10:35,802 --> 00:10:37,722
‐ [Trucker] Unit 101
delivery completed.

233
00:10:37,804 --> 00:10:39,314
‐ [Trucker] Units
53 to 72, completed.

234
00:10:39,389 --> 00:10:40,969
‐ [Trucker] Here we go!

235
00:10:41,099 --> 00:10:42,099
‐ Ah!
‐ Whoa!

236
00:10:44,477 --> 00:10:48,557
‐ Ah, wow, that was a
lot of pizza we moved.

237
00:10:48,648 --> 00:10:51,278
Have we made enough to
cover your debts yet?

238
00:10:51,359 --> 00:10:53,649
‐ Yes, I was able
to pay them all back

239
00:10:53,736 --> 00:10:55,066
with today’s receipts.

240
00:10:55,155 --> 00:10:56,705
‐ Do people like the pizza?

241
00:10:56,823 --> 00:10:58,453
‐ They do, it’s a huge hit,

242
00:10:58,533 --> 00:11:00,533
we’ve got a ton of
orders for tomorrow.

243
00:11:00,660 --> 00:11:04,160
‐ Here, Ranpha’s special
1000 spice pizza!

244
00:11:06,124 --> 00:11:07,634
It’s delicious.

245
00:11:10,503 --> 00:11:12,963
(screaming)

246
00:11:13,047 --> 00:11:15,337
Was it really that spicy?

247
00:11:15,425 --> 00:11:17,975
(screaming)

248
00:11:18,052 --> 00:11:20,352
Hurry up, oh, it’s my
turn, that’s enough!

249
00:11:20,430 --> 00:11:22,180
